dct_title_s: Official Indiana showing counties in different colors, townships, cities, villages, post offices, steam and electric railways with stations and distances between stations. Index with Population according to 1930 Federal Census
dct_description_sm: Full color maps of Indiana on both sides in two sheets. Shows villages, post offices, steam and electric railways with stations and distances between stations. Index with Population according to 1930 Federal Census. Inserts include Congressional Districts established 1931, list of state parks and points of interest, Description of Township LAND Survey.
Dimensions: 113 x 75 cm, on sheet 128 x 122 cm; Scale: Approximately 1:433,520. 7 miles to one inch.
